{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"46-harirar-katha-huna","title":"শৰীৰৰ কথা শুনো","description":"আমাৰ প্রত্যেকৰে এক সুন্দৰ শৰীৰ আছে। কিন্তু কেতিয়াবা আপোনালোকে সেই সুন্দৰ শৰীৰেনো কি কয় শুনিব বিচাৰিছেনে ? ","language":"Assamese","langCode":"as","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Tapashi Mazumdar Gagoi"],"illustrators":["Angie & Upesh"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/46-harirar-katha-huna"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700895/size3/19ca6ebcfc082bc86d63cf3227d13b74.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/700895/size6/19ca6ebcfc082bc86d63cf3227d13b74.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/565/size6/d69a115f0c159ea882793ba2cb41ff0a.jpg","text":"আজি মই পঢ়াশালিলৈ নাযাওঁ।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/566/size6/e67202d3c0724d1ae12f5525d9dc8856.jpg","text":"কিয়নো আজি ৰবিবাৰ।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/567/size6/50b694506f146bcdb0646ca8053f7a51.jpg","text":"আজি মই টিভি নাচাওঁ।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/568/size6/b8e641dba09c099282edc58af00491cf.jpg","text":"চাৰিওদিশে বিদ্যুৎ সংযোগ ব্যাহত হৈ আছে।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/569/size6/3ecaea9bd358488c9ade06643ca1ecd5.jpg","text":"আজি মই কি কৰিম?","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/570/size6/f3770f7efffc083fda79a2a9dfc12dc7.jpg","text":"আজি মই শৰীৰৰ অংগসমূহৰ কথা শুনিম।\nশৰীৰৰ কথা বাৰু শুনে নেকি?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/571/size6/afb864fb23f4c5a4b37f085b77998e93.jpg","text":"প্রথমে মই মনে মনে থাকিম। একেবাৰে চুপ্-চাপ্।\nযাতে মই শৰীৰৰ অংগসমূহৰ কথা শুনিব পাৰো।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/572/size6/fd74e5e6b88ab5328e4dc167ed19caa1.jpg","text":"এতিয়া মই উশাহ নিশাহৰ শব্দ শুনিব বিচাৰো।\nউশাহত... নিশাহত... উশাহত... নিশাহত...","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/573/size6/1c9e720d459b3ccf8cb58a0005633f99.jpg","text":"মই এতিয়া জোৰেৰে উশাহ লওঁচোন... \nখ.....ক!\nআৰু নিশাহ এৰি দিওঁ.... ফু....চ!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/574/size6/e44035c6ff05d3c34ed2a3cb85a199f6.jpg","text":"এইবাৰ মই হৃদপিণ্ডৰ শব্দ শুনিম\nধপ্... ধপ্... ধপ্...","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/575/size6/b33e0cc792cac701dd5bee3c6516c8d8.jpg","text":"আমি হৃদপিণ্ডৰ ধপ্ ধপনি সঘনাই আৰু জোৰেৰে শুনিবলৈ পাওঁনে?\nনিশ্চয়, যদি আমি ২০ বাৰ তল ওপৰকৈ জপিয়াও তেনেহ’লে পাম।","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/576/size6/1bbe179bec0c1fbc347d9ab5d699b2c7.jpg","text":"এতিয়া চোৱাচোন মোৰ হৃদপিণ্ডৰ\nধপ্\nধপনি সঘনাই হৈছে বা বাঢ়িছে। ধপ্... ধপ্... ধপ্...","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/577/size6/02ba00623563facb600ff79966b52b87.jpg","text":"যদি মই বুঢ়া আঙুলিটো হাতৰ তলুৱা আৰু বাহুৰ মাজত ধৰো তেনেহ’লে মই হৃদপিণ্ডৰ প্রতিটো\nধপ্\nধপনি শুনিবলৈ পাম। আঙুলিয়ে বাৰু শুনে নেকি?","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/578/size6/1443c997d29cf44512d1146a698cd5be.jpg","text":"মই মোৰ নিজৰ হাঁহি শুনিব পাৰো।\nহা:..হা: হা:..হা: হা:..হা: হা:..হা:","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/579/size6/275fab1b0e972aa9d8056ed203866692.jpg","text":"আৰু মোৰ কান্দোনও শুনিব পাৰো।\nউ...উ...উ...উ...উ...উ","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/580/size6/65228cb2933cbaa00789deb9a4b0bb16.jpg","text":"আৰু মোৰ হাত চাপৰিও\nতাপ্ তাপ্ তাপ্ তাপ্","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/581/size6/e71f8fe4b9679488059ae940be347ec3.jpg","text":"কেতিয়াবা-মই মোৰ পেটৰ শব্দও শুনিবলৈ পাওঁ\nগুৰ্...গুৰ্ গুৰ্...গুৰ্ গুৰ্...গুৰ্","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/582/size6/1274d06379e74a021d185815759b20e2.jpg","text":"পেটটোৱে তেতিয়া কি কয় জানানে?\nখাবলৈ দিয়া খাবলৈ দিয়া।","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/583/size6/c8917f7ecb0112d31da482d8d6c9795f.jpg","text":"মোৰ নাকটোৱে এতিয়া মায়ে পাকঘৰত বনাই থকা জেলেপীৰ শব্দ শুনিছে।   নাকেও শুনে নেকি?","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/584/size6/f8cd7c097e22a9bbb628b475b65ba8cc.jpg","text":"মোৰ শৰীৰৰ শব্দ শুনাটো সঁচাকৈয়ে হাস্যমধুৰ।\nএতিয়া মই মোৰ দাঁতেৰে চোবোৱা শব্দ শুনিবলৈ পাম।","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/585/size6/ece2e176e7eccf901f54a55093b6bf30.jpg","text":"মোৰ পেটটোৱে এতিয়া মায়ে বনোৱা গৰম ফৰম\nজেলেপী খাবৰ বাবে ৰৈ আছে।","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/586/size6/da1518e56b316dfee44438575a9db48d.jpg","text":"শৰীৰৰ অংগৰ সৈতে শব্দবোৰ\nমিলোৱা\nহাত                                 সুঁহুৰি\n \n \n \nওঠ                                  চপট্ চপট্\n \n                      \n \n \n \nভৰিৰ পতা                       তাপ্ তাপ্",